{"tid":329623,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"想孭起背囊去流浪，求意見","createTime":"2017-07-20T13:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T18:24:56.000Z","uid":51559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5dbf1419cfc43956a20423201a5a05f400e5514","tid":329623,"uid":51559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:51:01.000Z","msg":"20出頭，想下年畢業去，想圍住中國行一圈，即係越南個堆，最後經蒙古同中國落返黎<br />\n有冇人知大概要幾耐？<br />\n以下係考慮嘅野<br />\n1.乜都唔識，第一次<br />\n2.要放低學業同理想，但係唔去就三五七年內都冇機會再去<br />\n3.屋企可能需要我作為經濟支柱<br />\n主要係呢啲，諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8484acee19a6cb91f9294e951fa98b64915e7a6","tid":329623,"uid":51559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4788a261183979918f48b2db632f58a00303f522","tid":329623,"uid":71219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:21:17.000Z","msg":"1.  你唔踏出就冇第一次 網上好多資訊 <br />\n<br />\n2. 你一畢業就有足夠既錢去？<br />\n<br />\n3. 冇話要幾耐 係睇你想去幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 學生身份既你，依加屋企都係靠你？否則，大半年既經濟支柱應該唔太大影響<br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n5. 的確年齡愈大，工作穩定左，會更難下定決心去 <br />\n    所以想去就去吧 樓主 <br />\n    <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8544b60bc343505702739dd9c1c674cfe2a73073","tid":329623,"uid":126376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"加油樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 圍住中國行一個圈聽落幾吸引"},{"pid":"91198f4f3398830863f6bb9b99ffcf26b241ab54","tid":329623,"uid":126376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T